model
Class Action

java.lang.Object
  model.Action

public class Action
extends java.lang.Object

The action class abstracts an event. Each event needs at least a name, called a label. Optionally, a vector time and data fields can set. If datafields will be used, useDatafields must be set before compilation.

Author:
Sigurd Schneider
